{
  "texts": [
    "Another fully automated approach, based on a 'Symmetry plane' [9, 16, 33] although showed promising results for routine clinical use, may not be applicable in a routine clinical context owing to the inaccessibility of the in-house developed software.",
    "Despite a comprehensive search and selection of specific studies, this review was limited due to the methodological heterogeneity observed across the included studies, which precluded performing a meta-analysis.",
    "Additionally, a lack of standardized assessment of facial asymmetry was noted, which may have had an impact on the findings.",
    "In addition, many of the included studies did not adequately demonstrate the accuracy of the constructed MSP.",
    "Future prospective studies with an emphasis on the impact, accuracy, and clinical applicability of MSP construction techniques in cases of facial asymmetry are required."
  ]
}